					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13526907#post-4718482</guid>
				<title>Finally, an explanation for Crab Rave!</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13526907/scp-4936#post-4718482</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2020 19:58:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Nagiros</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4665703</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p style="text-align: center;"><em><a href="https://www.poetryfoundation.org/poetrymagazine/poems/44212/the-love-song-of-j-alfred-prufrock">I should have been a pair of ragged claws, scuttling across the floors of silent seas.</a></em></p> </blockquote> <p>Well, this has been bouncing around my sandbox for about a year now. It's far more lighthearted<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-751000-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup> than, well, <em>all</em> of my other articles, and it was a blast to write and rewrite.</p> <p><span style="font-size:75%;">Psst! If you're interested in essophysics, try out <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-4260">SCP-4260</a>!</span></p> <p>Thanks again to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dianaberry" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3444428&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="DianaBerry" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3444428)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dianaberry" >DianaBerry</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/trustyolvalet2" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5366711&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="TrustyOlValet2" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5366711)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/trustyolvalet2" >TrustyOlValet2</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="Veralta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" >Veralta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greyve" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4045981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="Greyve" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4045981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greyve" >Greyve</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/j-habsburg" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6607675&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="J Habsburg" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6607675)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/j-habsburg" >J Habsburg</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5722579&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1594690470" alt="Marcelles_Raynes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5722579)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" >Marcelles_Raynes</a></span>!</p> <p style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="https://youtu.be/LDU_Txk06tM">(Obligatory music link.)</a></strong></p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-751000-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. That is, depending on how you read one line in particular.</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
